**** ** *** ******** **** * **** **** *** ** ** ***** Over all experience is horrible front the time I have arrived. 
1. I made a pre booking appointment at 6 30pm and reached there at 6 30pm and informed the receptionist and they told me to wait for 30 minutes. And I go back to check on the status and to my surprise they ask me what is the issue and what you have come for. Wonderful treatment they gave. 

2. After patiently explaining them the situation, 5 mins later the lady comes and asks me for an ID proof for patient and without it we cannot proceed further. Which we never carry everyday to prove our identity to everyone and nothing was mentioned during appointment call. And I told them after I reach home would send the details. 

3. This time I approach this * * * * * * * * **** doctor DHARANI just to clarify one of the doubts I had and she IS NOT READY TO LISTEN AND CLARIFY MY DOUBT and shuts the door on my face with my wife inside who has communication barrier despite my wife telling her the same. And in the end she gives me some report which I didn't understand and have been trying to ask that Lady for the same and she starts yelling on me insulting me and my wife telling me "why should I explain it you" One wonderful answer from a Doctor DHARANI. I did not utter a bad word at her considering her old age and she calls me S T U P I D in the end. And all these happened there from 6 30 pm to close to 9pm and doesn't let me out without paying which is want they wanted.  

4. In the end I ask what's the point of booking an appointment and she says that is how they function. ******** **** ** *** **** ** ******* Strongly recommend DO NOT GO TO THIS PLACE. **** ** *** *** **** ***** ** ***** *** *** **** ***** ****** ****

*** ** **** **** **** ** **** ***. Though i had all probs of pregnancy like puking, fatigue etc I still enjoyed it cuz of ma baby and Dr. Dharani. I made d worst scenes cuz of the pain but she was so patient with me and made me feel so worth it. ***** **** ***** I'm so vry vry grateful to her. I didn't co-operate with her evn once durin ma labor bur she has gvn me the world's best gift ma dear son. God bless you Doc. **** **** *******
